  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CannotChangeException
    This exception is thrown when an argument is given a value a second time.
    CannotFindException
    thrown when an order could not be found
    IllegalInfo
    Thrown when an Info-object was invalid.
    InvalidTimeException
    Thrown when a used Time was invalid.
    NoPersonWithNameAndRoleException
    Thrown when a person with given name and role could not be found.
    NotAFactoryException
    Thrown when a given value was not a Factory when it needed to be one.
    NotLoggedInException
    Thrown when an action was tried when the LoginController was not logged in.
    TreatmentAlreadyAddedException
    Thrown when it is tried to add a Treatment that is already added.
    WrongTreatmentException
    Thrown when the wrong Treatment type was used
